  <p>The difference between month one and month six can be dramatic. Most users see no visible change in the first 2&ndash;3 weeks. By month three, results become apparent. By month six, they're often unmistakable. Don't stop early.</p>
</div>

<!-- ========== SIDE EFFECTS ========== -->
