<tr><td><strong>Systemic side effects</strong></td><td class="r">Low (injectables)</td><td>Only relevant for systemic peptides like BPC-157; requires medical supervision</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<div class="d-r">
  <div class="s">Important Safety Note</div>
  <p>Systemic peptide therapies (injections, oral peptides) should always be discussed with a qualified healthcare provider. Topical peptide serums carry minimal risk for most people, but patch testing is still recommended for new products.</p>
</div>

